<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船上冒着烟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比跳上船，彼得也跳了上去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他脚下一滑，掉进了运河里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水淹到了彼得的脖子，但他的脚碰不到河底！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当彼得努力抓住了船的边缘时，菲利斯也伸手抓住了他的头发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然彼得的头很疼，但菲利斯还是成功把他拉了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得跳到船上，鲍比也帮菲利斯上了船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比走向舱门，但是彼得大喊：“别去！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我身上已经湿了，我去。”他把鲍比推开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果是平时，彼得这样对她，她已经哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是今天她只是说：“不，彼得，我去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得绕过她，走下楼梯，进入浓烟里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他停下来，用湿手帕捂住嘴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他对鲍比喊：“没事儿，火不大！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他撒了谎，因为他不想让鲍比下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>舱内一片火光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得拿开手帕大喊：“小宝宝，你在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他被浓烟呛得咳嗽起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我看看！”鲍比在后面大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得把她往后推。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，小宝宝哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得在浓烟里找到了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抱起小宝宝时，却撞到了鲍比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狗对着他叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我找到了小宝宝。”彼得一边喊着一边跑上楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比顺着狗的声音摸到了它的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狗轻轻地咬了咬她的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比说：“来，我带你走。”她抱起狗跑上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得和鲍比抱着小宝宝和狗跳下了船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“彼得，把小宝宝给我。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你身上太湿了，会让他感冒的。你快去酒吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我衣服湿了，跑不动啊！”彼得说，“太重了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我去！菲利斯，你抱着小宝宝。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她往“玫瑰和王冠”酒吧跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酒吧里，一群人正在喝酒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比冲进去，大喊：“比尔！我找船工比尔！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酒吧里突然安静下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家举着杯子的手停在半空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比看到比尔的妻子玛利亚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的船着火了！”她大喊，“快走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人一下子跳起来：“宝贝！啊！我的小宝贝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您的宝宝很安全。”鲍比说，“狗也很安全。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比尔赶紧站起来，和他的妻子一起往运河跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比尔提着几桶水跳上了船，彼得也去帮他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一起把火扑灭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天已经很晚了，妈妈很担心孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，孩子们到家了，不过他们全身都湿透了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们告诉妈妈今天发生的事情，妈妈很欣慰，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>并允许他们接受比尔的礼物——第二天去乘坐比尔的船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，菲利斯、鲍比和彼得去了运河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在篮子里装了面包、芝士和火腿作为午餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一整天都待在比尔的船上，在温暖的阳光下，沿着运河来回航行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比尔先生对他们很友好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉孩子们，他们可以随时去钓鱼，他也会帮助他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当孩子们告诉妈妈这件事时，妈妈说：“看来你们又交了新的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>先是在铁路上，现在是在运河上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>